statements.sql: select `vakkal_number`, `co`.`date`, `c`.`companyname`, `i`.`name` as `item_name`, `order_item_id`, `m`.`name` as `marka_name`, `quantity`, `chamber`.`number` as `chamber_number`, `floor`.`number` as `floor_number`, `grid`.`number` as `grid_number`, `order_items`.`description`, (SELECT SUM(if(oi.type='inward',oi.quantity,0))-SUM(if(oi.type='outward',oi.quantity,0)) FROM order_items as oi WHERE oi.vakkal_number = order_items.vakkal_number and oi.item_id=order_items.item_id and oi.chamber_id=order_items.chamber_id and oi.floor_id=order_items.floor_id and oi.grid_id=order_items.grid_id and oi.deleted_at is null) AS balance_quantity from `order_items` left join `customer_orders` as `co` on `order_items`.`customer_order_id` = `co`.`customer_order_id` left join `customers` as `c` on `co`.`customer_id` = `c`.`customer_id` left join `items` as `i` on `order_items`.`item_id` = `i`.`item_id` left join `marka` as `m` on `order_items`.`marka_id` = `m`.`marka_id` left join `chamber` on `order_items`.`chamber_id` = `chamber`.`chamber_id` left join `floor` on `order_items`.`floor_id` = `floor`.`floor_id` left join `grid` on `order_items`.`grid_id` = `grid`.`grid_id` where `order_items`.`type` = 'inward' and ((`vakkal_number` like '%2024/10/102%')) and `co`.`customer_id` = '238' and `order_items`.`deleted_at` is null order by `i`.`name` asc, `m`.`name` asc, `vakkal_number` asc, `order_items`.`sort` asc
